F2mParams.title: F2mParams
F2mParams.description:
The polynomials are encoded as constant-size bitstrings of `m` bits.
Each bitstring is encoded as a big-endian byte array, i.e. bit 0 of the bit string is the bit 0 of the last byte,
bit 7 is bit 7 of the last byte, highest bit of the first byte is the last bit, etc.
